overview: November 16th, 2008 :: Eddie Kingston battles Claudio Castagnoli. Brodie Lee vs Steve "The Turtle" Weiner  6. Campeonatos de Parejas: The Osirian Portal vs Lince Dorado, Equinox  7. Eddie Kingston vs Claudio Castagnoli  8. title: Chikara Armdrags To Riches
